atb soc noc topo:
dsp ss0 to ss5(6 sys) iniu noc side connect to dsp_funnel_6ch input
dsp_funnel_6ch output connect to async bridge slv
async bridge slv output to async bridge mst
async bridge mst output to one input channel of right funnel(3 atb input channels)
camera ss connect to one channel of right funnel
mipi ss connect to last channel right funnel
right funnel output to debug ss

top(only contain iniu/tniu top side + network layer) harden partition cut:
node from dsp ss0 to ss5 to async bridge slv are all in one harden,use one top clk
node from async bridge mst to right funnel to debug ss and camera/mipi ss are all in another harden, use another top clk